This is a placeholder for the certificate template PDF.

To create a proper certificate template:

1. Design your certificate in Figma, Canva, or any design tool
2. Export as PDF
3. Place the file here as: public/certificate-template.pdf

The template should have placeholder positions for:
- Student name
- Project title
- Domain
- Certificate ID
- Issue date
- QR code (for verification URL)

The API route at /api/certificates/generate will load this template
and fill in the fields using pdf-lib.
